title: LUKE CAMPBELL IMMEDIATE REACTION TO RYAN GARCIA KNOCKOUT LOSS: "I'M HEARTBROKEN"
author: FightHype.com
description: FightHype.com is on hand in Dallas, Texas where lightweight sensation Ryan Garcia knocked out top contender Luke Campbell with a brutal body shot in the 7th round of their showdown. You don't want to miss what went down after the fight. Check it out!
